        <updateDate>2021-02-05T19:46:47Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p><b>Creating Helpful Incentives for Producing Semiconductors for America and Foundries Act</b></p> <p>This bill establishes measures to incentivize semiconductor and microelectronics manufacturing. These measures include creating (1) a financial assistance program for investment in semiconductor facilities and equipment, (2) a public-private partnership with the Department of Defense to ensure the development and production of secure microelectronics, and (3) a Multilateral Semiconductors Security Fund to support the development and adoption of secure semiconductors and semiconductor supply chains. </p>]]></text>
      </summary>
